import { Box, TextField } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import styles from './NewUserForm.style'
function NewUserForm() {
  return (
    <Box>
                                <Box>
                        
                                    <TextField type="name" class="form-control" id="name"/>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <TextField type="text" class="form-control" id="name"/>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <TextField type="number" class="form-control" id="addr"/>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <TextField type="text" class="form-control" id="addr"/>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <TextField type="text" class="form-control" id="addr"/>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <TextField type="text" class="form-control" id="addr"/>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <TextField type="text" class="form-control" id="addr"/>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <TextField type="tel" class="form-control" id="tel"/>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <select name="role" id="role">
                                        <option value="employee">Employee</option>
                                        <option value="sde1">SDE 1</option>
                                        <option value="sde2">SDE 2</option>
                                        <option value="sde3">SDE 3</option>
                                        <option value="pm">Project Manager</option>
                                        <option value="hr">Human Resource</option>
                                    </select>
                                </Box>
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <TextField type="date" id="date" name="date"/>
                                </Box>
                                
                                <Box>
                                    
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3"></textarea>
                                  </Box>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                            </Box>
  )
}

export default NewUserForm
